title: Even tot hier
overview: Niels van der Laan and Jeroen Woe, known from hit show 'De Kwis', are back on TV every Saturday night, March 16 with a new satirical program Even tot hier. Together with the Miguel Wiels Band, an ensemble of 7 singing actors, an expert and a musical greatness, all of this week's news will soon be reviewed. They literally try to make a performance of the week.
